===
Mai
===

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/zalando-stups/mai.svg?branch=master
   :target: https://travis-ci.org/zalando-stups/mai
   :alt: Build Status

.. image:: https://coveralls.io/repos/zalando-stups/mai/badge.svg
